Version GakuNin1.0 (2011-09-12)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Settings of the Extension]
  * Referer check and incremental search are made available on a server's settings.
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-11


[Releasing and Not Releasing the Information about Selected IdP by Using Referer Check]
  * When a DS server checks a referer while an Embedded DS screen is displayed, and the referer does 
    not exist within metadata, the Embedded DS does not release information about the last selected 
    IdP. 
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-6
  * When a referer cannot be obtained during a referer check, "!" sign will be displayed on the 
    screen and a warning message will be displayed by hovering a mouseover.
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-1
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-8
  * When a referer cannot be obtained during a referer check, a DS server creates SP cookies, and 
    information about the IdP will be referred to and displayed from the next time.


[IdP Search Functions by Using Incremental Search]
  * To implement by means of input check at intervals of 0.5 second
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-12 
  * To select an IdP from an IdP list by using an arrow key and transit to an IdP by pressing 
    Enter key
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-14
  * To allocate a reset function as a link to clear the textbox
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-17
  * To select an IdP automatically when it narrows down to one option by an incremental search
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-18
  * To handle access to a Central DS when Javascript is off
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-19
  * Behavior of hovering the mouse cursor to an IdP list
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-20
  * To add an arrow sign that enables display/hide an IdP list 
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-26
  * To enable narrowing down to an IdP list compatible with set-up SPs by using DiscoFeed functions
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-37
  * To clear an entry field by pressing Escape key    
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-38
  * To display a horizontal scroll bar when there are more IdP names than can be listed in an IdP list
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-39
  * To hide an IdP list when transferred from a textbox by pressing a Tab key
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-48
  * To enable a SP's setting file to set up the vertical length of an IdP list displayed by an 
    Embedded DS
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-50


[Modification of SWITCHwayf]
  * To modify a SP's setting file so that it can set up a path of cookies created by selecting an 
    IdP outside of the Federation
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-32
  * To modify the default value of a screen display setting for re-authentication set by a SP 
    (i.e. to enable the selection of an IdP list)
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-36
  * To modify the snippet.html so that embedded-wayf.js is not allowed to be casehed 
    - https://forge.gakunin.nii.ac.jp/jira/browse/DISCOVERY-42

